26#ifndef NetworkCacheSpeculativeLoadManager_h
27#define NetworkCacheSpeculativeLoadManager_h
28
29#if ENABLE(NETWORK_CACHE_SPECULATIVE_REVALIDATION)
30
31#include "NetworkCache.h"
32#include "NetworkCacheStorage.h"
33#include <WebCore/ResourceRequest.h>
34#include <wtf/HashMap.h>
35#include <wtf/Vector.h>
36#include <wtf/WeakPtr.h>
37
38namespace WebKit {
39
40namespace NetworkCache {
41
42class Entry;
43class SpeculativeLoad;
44class SubresourceInfo;
45class SubresourcesEntry;
46
47class SpeculativeLoadManager : public CanMakeWeakPtr<SpeculativeLoadManager> {
48 WTF_MAKE_FAST_ALLOCATED;
49public:
50 explicit SpeculativeLoadManager(Cache&, Storage&);
51 ~SpeculativeLoadManager();
52
53 void registerLoad(const GlobalFrameID&, const WebCore::ResourceRequest&, const Key& resourceKey, std::optional<NavigatingToAppBoundDomain>);
54 void registerMainResourceLoadResponse(const GlobalFrameID&, const WebCore::ResourceRequest&, const WebCore::ResourceResponse&);
55
56 typedef Function<void (std::unique_ptr<Entry>)> RetrieveCompletionHandler;
57
58 bool canRetrieve(const Key& storageKey, const WebCore::ResourceRequest&, const GlobalFrameID&) const;
59 void retrieve(const Key& storageKey, RetrieveCompletionHandler&&);
60
61private:
62 class PreloadedEntry;
63
64 static bool shouldRegisterLoad(const WebCore::ResourceRequest&);
65 void addPreloadedEntry(std::unique_ptr<Entry>, const GlobalFrameID&, std::optional<WebCore::ResourceRequest>&& revalidationRequest = std::nullopt);
66 void preloadEntry(const Key&, const SubresourceInfo&, const GlobalFrameID&, std::optional<NavigatingToAppBoundDomain>);
67 void retrieveEntryFromStorage(const SubresourceInfo&, RetrieveCompletionHandler&&);
68 void revalidateSubresource(const SubresourceInfo&, std::unique_ptr<Entry>, const GlobalFrameID&, std::optional<NavigatingToAppBoundDomain>);
69 void preconnectForSubresource(const SubresourceInfo&, Entry*, const GlobalFrameID&, std::optional<NavigatingToAppBoundDomain>);
70 bool satisfyPendingRequests(const Key&, Entry*);
71 void retrieveSubresourcesEntry(const Key& storageKey, WTF::Function<void (std::unique_ptr<SubresourcesEntry>)>&&);
72 void startSpeculativeRevalidation(const GlobalFrameID&, SubresourcesEntry&, bool, std::optional<NavigatingToAppBoundDomain>);
73
74 static bool canUsePreloadedEntry(const PreloadedEntry&, const WebCore::ResourceRequest& actualRequest);
75 static bool canUsePendingPreload(const SpeculativeLoad&, const WebCore::ResourceRequest& actualRequest);
76
77 Cache& m_cache;
78 Storage& m_storage;
79
80 class PendingFrameLoad;
81 HashMap<GlobalFrameID, RefPtr<PendingFrameLoad>> m_pendingFrameLoads;
82
83 HashMap<Key, std::unique_ptr<SpeculativeLoad>> m_pendingPreloads;
84 HashMap<Key, std::unique_ptr<Vector<RetrieveCompletionHandler>>> m_pendingRetrieveRequests;
85
86 HashMap<Key, std::unique_ptr<PreloadedEntry>> m_preloadedEntries;
87
88 class ExpiringEntry;
89 HashMap<Key, std::unique_ptr<ExpiringEntry>> m_notPreloadedEntries; // For logging.
90};
91
92} // namespace NetworkCache
93
94} // namespace WebKit
95
96#endif // ENABLE(NETWORK_CACHE_SPECULATIVE_REVALIDATION)
97
98#endif // NetworkCacheSpeculativeLoadManager_h
